{"id":24769,"date":"2024-02-29T13:13:50","date_gmt":"2021-08-30T07:43:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=24769"},"modified":"2024-07-25T19:32:19","modified_gmt":"2024-07-25T14:02:19","slug":"modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room\/","title":{"rendered":"8 Modern Sofa Set Designs Suitable For Every Living Room"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Check these eight modern sofa set designs to plan your living room renovation easily!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The idea of the perfect home varies from person to person. This is the space where you and your family return to after a long day at work to kick back, relax and get cosy. One of the significant parts of this relaxation is having a comfy sofa set, where you can relax and watch your favourite movie or web series, eat and chill, play with your kids or entertain guests when they come over. So, the sofa not only is a functional focal point, but it also works as a centrepiece that completes the living room. Therefore, sofa sets need to be aesthetically attractive yet functional.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, while choosing a sofa set, there is a mind-boggling number of choices available in the market: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/l-shaped-sofa-designs\/\">L-shaped sofa<\/a>, U-shaped sofa, minimalist sofa, over-the-top maximalist sofa, two-seater, three-seater, five-seater, loveseat or even sofa bed \u2014 the options are unlimited. Here are some trending modern sofa set designs you should consider for the comfort of your dreams.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Add Old-World Charm To Your Living Room With A Modern Wooden Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wooden sofa set doesn\u2019t necessarily have to be flashy or over the top. Nowadays, wooden furniture is trending among homeowners and even renters. Like the wooden sofa set shown in the image below, which has a sleek structure. Its unique design makes the room look bigger and airier than it is. Wooden sofa sets come in various designs and wood types. However, this furniture needs proper maintenance, like polishing, if made of solid wood since they are more prone to attract termites. Therefore, if you consider a modern wooden sofa set, opt for engineered wood over solid wood.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121952\/living-room-with-modern-wooden-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Modern wooden sofa set design in living room\" class=\"wp-image-24777\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121952\/living-room-with-modern-wooden-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121952\/living-room-with-modern-wooden-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121952\/living-room-with-modern-wooden-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121952\/living-room-with-modern-wooden-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Sleek wooden sofa sets like this brings a sense of minimalism<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Increase Seating Space With a Modern L-Shaped Sectional<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your living room has space to spare, then a modern L-shaped sofa or sectional is the perfect addition to your home. With one side open, these sofa sets can be rearranged and are versatile. Increase the seating when hosting a house party or arrange it as an extra bed when a guest sleeps.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The L-shaped sectional, shown in the first picture, is perfect for a bigger open space apartment or a villa. The grey fabric is soothing and can go with any colour scheme.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the other hand, the beige couch\u2019s simplicity perfectly complements the stylish charcoal gallery wall behind in the second picture. The elegant overhead chandelier completes the aesthetic of the living space, giving it an ultra-luxurious look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121959\/modern-l-shaped-sectional-set-design-in-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Modern l-shaped sectional sofa in living room to increase seating space\" class=\"wp-image-24778\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121959\/modern-l-shaped-sectional-set-design-in-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121959\/modern-l-shaped-sectional-set-design-in-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121959\/modern-l-shaped-sectional-set-design-in-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121959\/modern-l-shaped-sectional-set-design-in-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The simplicity of the sofa set is appealing<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Let The Conversations Flow With Modern U-Shaped Sofa Set<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are a part of a large family, your home needs a large U-shaped sofa set since it offers a lot of seating. A central sofa connects two equal-sized side sofas in this type of set, giving it a U-shape. The picture below shows that the large creme colour U-shaped sectional is perfect for this family room. It is accentuated by two large French doors that let nature in. Additionally, the unique built-in TV unit and massive chandelier complete this warm and stylish family room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122024\/modern-u-shaped-sofa-set-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Modern u-shaped sofa set design for living room\" class=\"wp-image-24781\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122024\/modern-u-shaped-sofa-set-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122024\/modern-u-shaped-sofa-set-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122024\/modern-u-shaped-sofa-set-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122024\/modern-u-shaped-sofa-set-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Opt for a U-shaped sofa set if you have a big family or often entertain many guests over<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"2898\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic.jpg\" alt=\"Infographic breaks down modern sofa set designs for living room\" class=\"wp-image-57937\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic-97x300.jpg 97w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic-332x1024.jpg 332w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic-768x2368.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic-50x154.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic-498x1536.jpg 498w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic-664x2048.jpg 664w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/25193026\/modern-sofa-set-designs-for-living-room-infographic-150x462.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Three-Seater Sofa For Small Families<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The modern three-seater sofa is commonly opted for by newly married couples or those who have small families. Nowadays, sofas are widely made as three-seaters. Get inspired by this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/simple-living-room-designs\/\">simple living room design<\/a> shown in the picture below. The mid-sized living room looks complete with this modern-looking rustic grey three-seater sofa with a one-seater couch and large pouffe. While the floor lamp and the tall indoor plant add height to the room, the dark area rug and three-part <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/modern-coffee-table\/\">modern coffee table<\/a> add dimension to the light colour scheme of the living room. This modern living room design can easily be DIY-ed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122015\/modern-three-seater-sofa-for-small-families.jpg\" alt=\"Modern three-seater grey sofa for small families\" class=\"wp-image-24780\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122015\/modern-three-seater-sofa-for-small-families.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122015\/modern-three-seater-sofa-for-small-families-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122015\/modern-three-seater-sofa-for-small-families-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122015\/modern-three-seater-sofa-for-small-families-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Let your inner interior designer out with this modern three-seater sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Timeless Leather Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/leather-sofa-design-ideas\/\">Leather sofas<\/a> are timeless. But that doesn\u2019t necessarily have to be boring. As shown in the picture below, the leather couch perfectly complements the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/luxury-living-room-design-ideas\/\">luxury living room<\/a>. White marble flooring, dark wooden false ceiling, fancy marble-top coffee table, and massive mirror work on the wall all come together elegantly with this majestic high-back brown sofa. The living room screams luxury.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121944\/leather-sofa-design-in-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Leather sofa set design perfectly complements the luxury living room\" class=\"wp-image-24776\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121944\/leather-sofa-design-in-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121944\/leather-sofa-design-in-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121944\/leather-sofa-design-in-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121944\/leather-sofa-design-in-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Leather sofas speak for themselves in an opulent living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sofa Designs for Small Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your apartment has a space crunch, make most of the available space by bringing in an L-shaped sectional. Since they are versatile, you can remove the adjustable part, create extra separate seating, or use it as a table. Take inspiration from the picture below. Look how the teal sectional and baby blue lounge chair make the otherwise simple white room look vibrant. The picture gallery wall works as the perfect room decor, and the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-floor-lamps\/\">floor lamp<\/a> adds height. In rooms painted in light colours, greenery is a must to sprinkle some life \u2014 therefore, the potted indoor plants are placed in the corner.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122031\/sofa-designs-for-small-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"L-shaped sectional sofa designs for small living room\" class=\"wp-image-24782\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122031\/sofa-designs-for-small-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122031\/sofa-designs-for-small-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122031\/sofa-designs-for-small-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30122031\/sofa-designs-for-small-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A perfect design for a small living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Five-Seater Sofas For Large Homes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The tufted blue five-seater sofa shown in the picture below is an excellent example of how vibrant colours can be incorporated in an apartment with an otherwise muted colour palette. The massive plush area rug, high back lounge chair and wooden coffee and side tables have given the living room a cosy, stylish vibe. This five-seater sofa can be a great addition to a large apartment or modern villa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121936\/five-seater-sofas-for-large-homes.jpg\" alt=\"5 seater sofas are perfect for a large living room\" class=\"wp-image-24775\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121936\/five-seater-sofas-for-large-homes.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121936\/five-seater-sofas-for-large-homes-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121936\/five-seater-sofas-for-large-homes-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121936\/five-seater-sofas-for-large-homes-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Five-seater sofas are perfect for a large living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/loveseat-design\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Loveseat Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Compact And Versatile Sofa Beds<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you live in a studio or 1BHK apartment that doesn\u2019t have much space for a separate living room, sofa beds are perfect for you. These are now popular among young professionals who wish to have a sofa and a comfy bed but have a limited budget. Sofa beds can easily hold two-three people in the sofa position. At night, flatten it out to make a comfortable bed. These can also be used as a guest bed if someone comes over.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121929\/compact-and-versatile-sofa-beds-in-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"A compact and versatile sofa bed is ideal for a 1 bhk apartment that doesn't have much space\" class=\"wp-image-24774\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121929\/compact-and-versatile-sofa-beds-in-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121929\/compact-and-versatile-sofa-beds-in-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121929\/compact-and-versatile-sofa-beds-in-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30121929\/compact-and-versatile-sofa-beds-in-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A sofa bed is an easy solution when you have a guest over<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Sofas are available for every price range, colour scheme, fabric, and outfit every home \u2014 from a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/studio-apartment-interior-design-ideas\/\">studio apartment<\/a> to a luxury villa. There\u2019s indeed something for everyone. But if you are confused about which style will suit your space, let our designers do their magic. Take a free consultation today. Also, don&#8217;t forget to shower your love for these designs in the comments section below!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div cla